        The DAC in [Ukraine](https://open-archive.org/news/memo-from-kharkiv) works to center eyewitness accounts, reflections, and testimonies on the war. They use this compelling evidence to shed light on the true toll of Russia’s violence against them. By amplifying these narratives, they provide a comprehensive understanding of the conflict’s ramifications, informing more effective strategies for peacebuilding and rebuilding. 
    </span>
